  <trk>
    <name>MXP-L2 — Lake Como &amp; Stelvio Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MXP and ride into the Lake Como &amp; Stelvio. Hit Bellagio — 230m and Bormio — 1225m. Loop back to MXP over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
